videos.description: Michigan guard Jordan Poole jabs, steps back and knocks down a 3-pointer, finishing off the 4-point play with a free throw.
videos.headline: Poole nails contested 3 for 4-point play

videos.description: Charles Matthews pokes the ball away from  Northwestern and Zavier Simpson leaves it for him at the other end to extend Michigan's 1st-half lead.
videos.headline: Michigan's Matthews rises up for breakaway slam

videos.description: Jon Teske throws a cross-court pass to Big Ten Freshman of the Week Ignas Brazdeikis for a 3-pointer vs. Northwestern.
videos.headline: Michigan freshman Brazdeikis knocks down contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Northwestern's Anthony Gaines puts back Vic Law's missed layup, then A.J. Turner finishes an and-1 layup off a steal to narrow Michigan's lead.
videos.headline: Northwestern claws back vs. Michigan with back-to-back buckets

videos.description: Jordan Poole attacks the lane and rises up for a wide-open dunk to give Michigan a late lead over Northwestern late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Poole gives Michigan late lead with slam

videos.description: Northwestern's Ryan Taylor pulls up for a deep 3-pointer the buzzer vs. Michigan, but it bounces off the rim as the Wolverines remain perfect.
videos.headline: Michigan survives after missed 3 at buzzer
